Nazenin/Veleria Hatun is a fictional character from Muhteshem Yuzyil. It is not historically clear who the mother of Raziye Sultan was. Since Sultan Suleiman never married anyone apart from Hurrem and Raziye is certainly not recorded among Hurrems offspring, Raziye is the daughter of an unknown concubine. She probably died with her elder brothers Mahmud and Murad in 1521.
